{"tid":594252,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"普巴做愛叫聲太大被投訴","createTime":"2018-03-15T16:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T16:58:27.000Z","uid":1426,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c7247f0e7de7a0fe4b7f933d85789c7e9d60fcb7","tid":594252,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T16:20:13.000Z","msg":"據英國媒體披露，曼聯球星普巴因為在酒店內「動靜太大」遭到其他客人投訴，他與非洲女歌星丹西婭的幽會，成為了媒體議論的熱點。<br />\n<br />\n　　《太陽報》披露，普巴和新歡丹西婭在曼徹斯特著名的五星級酒店「Lowry」相會，但客人對他們鬧出的聲響十分不滿。一位酒店客人對該報說：「我們和他們房間相鄰，都在三層，能看到他們進入通道盡頭的房間。我淩晨兩點才睡，而他們的房內傳來音樂聲和笑聲。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「後來一切安靜下來，但在淩晨三、四點之間，又傳來了呻吟和叫喊聲，他們不在乎有沒有人聽到，而且沒完沒了，聽起來就像是一部色情片一樣，有幾次，我們清楚的聽到&lsquo;保羅、寶貝！&rsquo;，很煩人。不可能聽不到，因為她聲音太大了。」<br />\n<br />\n　　《太陽報》在該酒店的一個線人，甚至全程跟蹤「監聽」普巴與戀人的活動。「我最初看到普巴和丹西婭在一起，是在9月24日晚，第一次聽到叫床聲是在第二天淩晨一點到兩點之間。而在9月27、28和30日夜裡，我同樣能聽到，大約是淩晨四點。最初我以為一個晚上就結束了，可卻總是重覆上演。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「在曼聯一場比賽之後，這一情況再次出現，這次更響了，聽起來很狂野，持續了兩個小時。第二天我看到了普巴的女孩，認出是丹西婭，她確實很漂亮。」<br />\n<br />\n　　對於《太陽報》這一報導，曼聯方面予以了否認，球會一位發言人說：「這完全是不真實的， Lowry酒店沒有收到對於普巴的投訴。」<br />\n<br />\n　　值得一提的是， Lowry酒店裡還住著另一位與普巴有關聯的「大牌」：曼聯教練摩連奴，摩帥入主紅魔以來，尚未找到合適的房產，一直住在這家酒店，已有快4個月了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/3/2016/10/18/2/25ec252aea6c45e6a685be0e69b501de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F3%2F2016%2F10%2F18%2F2%2F25ec252aea6c45e6a685be0e69b501de.jpg&h=b5313b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_o05.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_o05.gif&h=ee0392a1&s={SIZE}\" />普巴好勁"},{"pid":"8dccbf491783a2dd2c53d859c5b4b085e23d6105","tid":594252,"uid":48104,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T16:24:33.000Z","msg":"一睇就知條女好波過普巴"},{"pid":"73fda204733e373796b6ee53108ae57adba33bb8","tid":594252,"uid":83748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T16:26:39.000Z","msg":"個咀超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517d95b575dcf8a2193be96565f94060b85e7b18","tid":594252,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T16:27:26.000Z","msg":"力架剩係識扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8adb66c9de90714d6d362eb08ca2b7b36819c7","tid":594252,"uid":17496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T16:27:30.000Z","msg":"打假波"},{"pid":"f40161836a494ef6cdfce4e0faf24fa2c11be4ef","tid":594252,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T15:56:42.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"3f409ea3646f54080f8563d9b33cd809a603b9ad","tid":594252,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:12:58.000Z","msg":"bigtits ebony<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a89f0066262fc62db1d39389b7a1bb36a0d021","tid":594252,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:13:32.000Z","msg":"仲未有4p 虛脫gif"},{"pid":"fa5035c2211b870f1b56b879d382f5192222c33a","tid":594252,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:13:32.000Z","msg":"N6"},{"pid":"bb70c7a54c6c3caabe9d3ac38f0b3da51d84b75e","tid":594252,"uid":54104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:14:42.000Z","msg":"漂白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272a9a19defb6c39a4664f3555d47e5f7e45ffe1","tid":594252,"uid":25939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T16:54:06.000Z","msg":"段野咁熟既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce8affda00bf0c2f8b4ba6380316b85d4174a16","tid":594252,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T17:05:46.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"0765a16307707d00ec158a97eda56445e0fe2b25","tid":594252,"uid":52476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T16:58:27.000Z","msg